Arụgharịala Ụlọakwụkwọ Central School Obioma nke na ndị obodo niile na enwezi aṅụrị ugbua.
Ya bụ ụlọakwụkwọ dakasiburu adaka oge gara nke kpatara na ụmụ ankwụkwọ na-agụ akwụkwu n'iro.
Etu mmepe ụlọakwụkwọ n'Abia steeti si gaa taa
Anambra Saturday School: Ụmụakwụkwọ agara akwụkwọ taa?
Nwa afọ obodo Obioma bụ Prince Ike Chioke jiri maka ahụhụ ụmụ akwụkwọ na-ata wepụta onwe ya wee rụgharịa ụlọakwụkwọ ahụ niile.
Mazi ike Chioke kwuru na ebum n'obi ya bụ ka onye ọbụla nwee ohere igụ akwụkwọ dị mma na primari nakwa sekondari.
Ndị soro kpee ekpere ma gbaa ama mmepe ahụ bụ nwunye gọvanọ Edo steeti bụ Betty Obaseki nakwa Auxilliary Bishop nke Enugwu katolik diocese bụ Bishop Ernest Obodo.
Lee ka o si ga ebe a.
